data.who-are-we#Who are we: Photo from SAFMC 2024 Award Ceremony in SUTD Who are weWe are a club of students who are are keen on developing and building drones for various applications. Although our main focus is on building and flying Multi-Rotors of varying levels of autonomy, our members are generally interested in remote controlled (RC) vehicles such as drones, cars and boats and will ocassionally dabble in these fields as well.
